external_knowledge:
- "Treasures hidden in the digital vault" refers to files stored in a database;
- "Identity of those who have planted the seeds" refers to the names of users who uploaded the files;
- "Gardens in which they bloom" refers to the projects to which the files belong.

sql:
SELECT created_date
FROM file_tags
WHERE file_id = 1 AND tag_id = 1 AND created_date = '2023-01-05' AND created_by = 0;

SELECT file_id, MAX(version) AS latest_version
FROM file_versions
GROUP BY file_id;
